	<div style="text-align:right;">
		CORRÊA, Jessica Audrey Feijó<sup>1</sup>; CESARO, Giovanna<sup>2</sup>; ROSA, Edvaldo Antonio Ribeiro<sup>3</sup>; ROSA, Rosimeire Takaki<sup>4</sup>; SOARES JÚNIOR, Paulo César<sup>5</sup>; LAURINDO, Carlos Augusto Henning<sup>6</sup>; MANDUCA, Rachel Tereza Rigotti<sup>7</sup>; LUCIANO, Fernando Bittencourt<sup>8</sup>		<BR>
